Context: Alumni can create or log in to a GRAD ACCOUNT on GBCareers platform to access career support services, including resume and cover letter assistance, interview skills training, job-search help, and career development. Contact Career Support at 416-415-2000 or ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The information on the website is subject to change without notice. George Brown College fee requirements should be verified by students.
